<div class="safety-standard-info">
  <h4>EN 14960:2019 Anchor Requirements</h4>
  <p>The number of anchors required is calculated based on the total area of the equipment.</p>
  
  <div class="formula-box">
    <strong>Formula:</strong> <code>Required Anchors = (Area × 2.15) rounded up</code>
    <br><em>Example: 20m² equipment requires ⌈20 × 2.15⌉ = 43 anchors</em>
  </div>

  <h5>Anchor Specifications:</h5>
  <ul>
    <li>Ground-level anchoring points (low anchors)</li>
    <li>Elevated anchoring points for tall structures (high anchors)</li>
    <li>30° to 45° angle to ground</li>
    <li>1600 Newton pull strength minimum</li>
  </ul>
</div>